\t\t\n\t<\/div><!-- #oceanwp-mobile-menu-navbar -->\n\n\t\n\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-1aea8ab elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"1aea8ab\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-e74a9ba\" data-id=\"e74a9ba\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-72bfe0a elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"72bfe0a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h1 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">My Grandfather was a carpenter\n...and I am a carpenter<\/h1>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2e08899 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2e08899\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The Professional Craftsmen at tOdd-jobs are ready to handle all your interior and exterior carpentry needs for your home or business. We have perfected our carpentry skills through years of experience, training, and dedication.<\/p><p>Our Craftsmen can make your interior and exterior carpentry projects come to life. We&#8217;ll listen to your desires and evaluate your carpentry needs to help you choose the right materials and best designs for your home.<\/p><p>All of our Craftsman take great pride in their abilities to modernize or improve your home&#8217;s look with everything from basic structural repairs to intricate finish work. When they complete a carpentry job, you will enjoy it for many years down the road.<\/p><p>Every carpentry project requires expertise to bring forth the results that will help all your jobs blend together perfectly. Interior and exterior carpentry updates added value to your home. The beauty is in the detailed work that our experienced carpenters work meticulously to provide.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-433694f\" data-id=\"433694f\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cbc3b01 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"cbc3b01\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"497\" height=\"750\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/todd-jobs.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/6a625a6301b5cd3627529dda10a97828.jpg?fit=497%2C750&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1766\" alt=\"Carpenter near me\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/todd-jobs.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/6a625a6301b5cd3627529dda10a97828.jpg?w=497&amp;ssl=1 497w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/todd-jobs.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/6a625a6301b5cd3627529dda10a97828.jpg?resize=199%2C300&amp;ssl=1 199w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 497px) 100vw, 497px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-189096f elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"189096f\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-70fa43d\" data-id=\"70fa43d\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-036982b elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"036982b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"835\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/todd-jobs.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/image.jpg?fit=835%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1764\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/todd-jobs.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/image.jpg?w=1245&amp;ssl=1 1245w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/todd-jobs.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/image.jpg?resize=245%2C300&amp;ssl=1 245w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/todd-jobs.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/image.jpg?resize=835%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 835w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/todd-jobs.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/image.jpg?resize=768%2C941&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 835px) 100vw, 835px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-c0e7f93\" data-id=\"c0e7f93\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-568d1b3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"568d1b3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Interior carpentry projects often complete the look of a home, while adding valuable details and functionality improvements. When you choose tOdd-jobs Handyman Services, you experience unparalleled professionalism and quality. Ace Handyman Services offers a collective of talented carpenters that receive ongoing training.<\/p><p>Our work may involve simple mouldings or complex columns with recessed panels and one-of-a-kind profiles. No matter the project, our attention to detail, quality of work and inventive solutions is easily recognizable.\u00a0<\/p><ul><li>Beautiful carpentry adds value to your home!<\/li><li>No project is too large or too small for our Craftsmen.<\/li><li>High quality finished look to help you love your home!<\/li><li>Our professional carpenters bring decades of hands on experience.<\/li><li>100% satisfaction guarantee on every project<\/li><\/ul><p>Interior carpentry tasks can include: installation of window and door trim work; interior doors; crown, chair, and baseboard mouldings; wainscoting, decorative-beam ceilings; mantels; straight-run and radius stairways; and custom cabinetry and book cases.<\/p><p>Take advantage of years of experience in every facet of carpentry for your home. Our Craftsmen are up-to-date with all the current styles and always work with important safety measures in mind.<\/p><p>What do you have in mind? New kitchen counters and cabinets? New insulation and sheetrock? How about crown moulding for the living room, or a custom book shelf or shelving for the office? Stair railing, treads and balusters?<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-3fc7a49 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"3fc7a49\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-4b0e346\" data-id=\"4b0e346\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b817f51 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b817f51\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"ui-id-2\" class=\"content ui-accordion-content ui-corner-bottom ui-helper-reset ui-widget-content ui-accordion-content-active\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"exterior\" aria-hidden=\"false\"><p>When your project necessitates stepping outside your home, we are experienced! Ready for an elegant deck, trellis, porch, or fence? Maybe a custom outdoor kitchen or gazebo?<\/p><p>Carpentry projects require the knowledge of a skilled Craftsman. Precision and a pride in one&#8217;s work are the key for carpentry jobs. Our professional carpenters will leave your home looking beautiful with great finish-out that enhances the beauty of your home.<\/p><ul><li>Deck &amp; Patio Construction<\/li><li>Soffits<\/li><li>Outdoor Kitchen<\/li><li>Gazebo Construction<\/li><li>Shutters around a window.<\/li><li>Build an Awning<\/li><\/ul><p>Exterior carpentry makes improvements not only to home design but also to the function of the home. Experienced carpentry Craftsmen know that the key to spectacular interior and exterior carpentry is having the best and the sharpest tools for doing precision work. With their skill, your job will be done right and within budget.<\/p><p>Call our offices today to enhance learn more about our exterior carpentry experience. What better project to create or upgrade your home to enjoy family and entertain friends.<\/p><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-44c1004\" data-id=\"44c1004\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-59b8af3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"59b8af3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"650\" height=\"456\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/todd-jobs.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/Gazebo-Bayside-10ft-1-web.jpg?fit=650%2C456&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1767\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/todd-jobs.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/Gazebo-Bayside-10ft-1-web.jpg?w=650&amp;ssl=1 650w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/todd-jobs.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/Gazebo-Bayside-10ft-1-web.jpg?resize=300%2C210&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-14867cd elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"14867cd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"481\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/todd-jobs.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/